===Adjective===
'''dynamic'''

# [[changeable|Changeable]]; [[fluid]]; not [[steady]]; in [[motion]].
#:''The environment is '''dynamic''', changing with the years and the seasons.''
#:''He was a '''dynamic''' and engaging speaker.''
# [[Able]] to [[change]] -- in the special context of computer programming languages.
# Powerful

